{{#> base_layout}}
<h2>Your MFA Backup Codes</h2>
<p>Save these backup codes in a secure location. Each code can only be used once to sign in if you lose access to your
    authenticator app.</p>

<div class="warning-box">
    <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>⚠️ Keep these codes safe</strong></p>
    <p style="margin: 8px 0 0 0;">Store them in a password manager or write them down and keep in a secure place. Don't
        share these codes with anyone.</p>
</div>

<div class="code-box">
    <div class="backup-codes">
        {{#each codes}}
        <span class="backup-code">{{this}}</span>
        {{/each}}
    </div>
</div>

<p class="muted">If you lose access to your authenticator and don't have these codes, you may be locked out of your
    account.</p>
{{/base_layout}}